<html>
<head>
    <title>Ilan Admin - Reset Password</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style type="text/css">
    body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333333;
    }
    a {
        color: #dc2626;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 26px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0;
        text-align: center;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
        color: #0c1927;
        margin: 20px 0;
        text-align: center;
        letter-spacing: 3px;
    }
    p {
        margin: 0 0 20px;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        overflow: hidden;
        border-color: #333333;
    }
    .email-header {
        background-color: #dc2626;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .email-body {
        padding: 30px;
    }
    .email-footer {
        background-color: #fafafa;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #545252;
    }
    .admin-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #dc2626;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 4px 12px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .warning-box {
        background-color: #fef3c7;
        border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .warning-box p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #92400e;
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="email-header">
        <h1>üîê Admin Password Reset</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Body -->
    <div class="email-body">
        <span class="admin-badge">ADMIN ACCOUNT</span>
        <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>
        We received a request to reset your administrator password. Use the OTP code below to reset it:
        </p>

        <h2><%= otp %></h2>

        <p>
        Please enter this code on the password reset page within the next <strong>5 minutes</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="warning-box">
            <p>‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Security Notice:</strong> If you did not request a password reset, please secure your account immediately and contact the system administrator.</p>
        </div>

        <p>
        Best regards,<br />
        <strong>The Ilan Admin Team</strong>
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="email-footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from Ilan Admin System. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Ilan. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
